BLUETOOTHCTL(1)                                    General Commands Manual                                   BLUETOOTHCTL(1)

NNAAMMEE
       bluetoothctl - bluetooth control tool

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
       bblluueettooootthhccttll

DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       bblluueettooootthhccttll is bluetooth control tool

UUSSAAGGEE
       bluetoothctl [options]

       Help Options:
         --hh, ----hheellpp Show help options

       Application Options:
         --vv, ----vveerrssiioonn Show version information and exit
         --aa, ----aaggeenntt==CCAAPPAABBIILLIITTYY Register agent handler

AAUUTTHHOORR
       This  manual page was written by Nobuhiro Iwamatsu <iwamatsu@debian.org>, for the Debian GNU/Linux system (but may be
       used by others).

